        "description": "<p><em>Yes Sire</em> is a strategic simulation set in medieval times and custom-made for smart speakers. You play the role of a king making yes or no decisions that are presented to you by a court assistant and confidante. The goal is to maintain balance in the kingdom by maintaining your wealth and influence meters between 0 and 100. Each question that is presented, regarding various military, economic, and personal matters, can reduce or increase these two stats. If your influence or wealth becomes too high or too low, the emperor will have you exiled or executed.</p>\n<p>The game is reminiscent of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/80569/reigns/\">Reigns</a>. Players have the option of buying a <em>Wicked Witch</em> expansion pack through an in-app purchase on their echo device. Players that can last 40 turns will be awarded a second expansion pack, the <em>Admiral DiCosta</em> expansion pack. Each expansion pack adds an additional 40-50 questions to the base game. The only two words players need to use are \"yes\" or \"no\".</p>",
